              Date: TBD
    v0.2    - TBD; 
              Date: TBD

    v1.0    - Stable release; 
              Date: TBD 

 4. Limitations
    v0.1    - Tested only in Firefox (newest Version, currently 11.0)
            - non "responsive" design -> not suitable for different platforms
              like smartphones or tablets

